  "description": "These parts extend Zometool by allowing you to construct blue lengths by adding struts, without introducing distracting extra balls.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe parts are sprued together, to reduce the cost.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe default material is blue, but I don&#39;t think the blue is very close to the Zometool blue. You might be better off buying in white, and dying or painting the struts.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;",
